                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">police-constable</hi> 88.) I produce the certificate of the prisoner's former conviction (<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—he is the man.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was taken very bad, I never saw the lead, nor had any thing on my person.</p>
